Peter Bull https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Bull 0 Peter Cecil Bull, (21 March 1912 – 20 May 1984) was a British character actor who appeared in supporting roles in such film classics as The African Queen, Tom Jones and Dr. Strangelove.
